{"tid":851380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冥幣RIP】人行：本月15日起下調人民幣存款準備金率1個百分點","createTime":"2018-10-07T05:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T06:20:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81fe58840e993809f5dcfe63df7c475a8a1f1808","tid":851380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1421706_1_L_20181007125012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1421706_1_L_20181007125012.jpg&h=ec8e0eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行宣布，本月15日開始下調人民幣存款準備金率1個百分點，當日到期的中期借貸便利 MLF不再續做。<br />\n<br />\n人行表示，為進一步支援實體經濟發展，優化商業銀行和金融市場的流動性結構，降低融資成本，引導金融機構繼續加大對小微企業、民營企業及創新型企業支持力度，決定下調大型商業銀行、股份制商業銀行、城市商業銀行、非縣域農村商業銀行、外資銀行人民幣存款準備金率1個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n人行強調將繼續實施穩健中性的貨幣政策，不搞大水漫灌，注重定向調控，保持流動性合理充裕，引導貨幣信貸和社會融資規模合理增長，為高品質發展和供給側結構性改革營造適宜的貨幣金融環境。"},{"pid":"a8098ee3362a705eb96db534f3a4efcb2f8ec0f6","tid":851380,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"5毛小學程度唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b390a9750f53d5934b4cbb1751f89536352a92f","tid":851380,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"又贏我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3ce67d0fe908fc359738ca36cd076b515d508b","tid":851380,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"又放水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a25c6c96796945fad44e0d62d3c8a8e44b5529","tid":851380,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":